n          </div>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n  <div class=\"subPage_con\">\n    <aside class=\"sub_left\">\n\n     \n      \n      <div class=\"sub_leftTitle\"><h2>教师队伍</h2></div>\n\n      <ul class=\"sub_nav\" id=\"SubMenu\">\n                         <li><a href=\"../index.htm\">教师</a></li>\n                                   <li><a href=\"../../zgkxyys/index.htm\">中科院院士</a></li>\n                                   <li><a href=\"../../rcjh/index.htm\">人才计划</a></li>\n                                  <li class=\"sub_has\">\n          <a href=\"../../bsh/index.htm\">博士后</a>\n          <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"skipBtn down\"></a>\n          <div class=\"subNavs\">\n                <dl>\n                                  \n    <dd><a href=\"../../bsh/zzbsh/index.htm\">在站博士后</a></dd>\n        \n                                   \n    <dd><a href=\"../../bsh/czbsh/index.htm\">出站博士后</a></dd>\n        \n                               </dl>\n            </div></li>\n                                       <li><a href=\"../../fwjs/index.htm\">访问教授</a></li>\n                                   <li><a href=\"../../js/index.htm\">教辅行政</a></li>\n                                   <li><a href=\"../../ltx/index.htm\">离退休</a></li>\n                                   <li><a href=\"../../yyhn/index.htm\">永远怀念</a></li>\n                        </ul>\n    \n      <ul class=\"subRepidList\">\n        <!--li>\n          <div class=\"subiconBox\">\n            <span class=\"subicon\"><img src=\"../../../images/icon1.png\"></span>\n            <h3><a href=\"../../../ggkfssnbdsxcjz1/index.htm\">北大数学成就展</a></h3>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li-->\n          <div class=\"subiconBox\">\n            <span class=\"subicon\"><img src=\"../../../images/icon2.png\"></span>\n            <h3><a href=\"../../../rcyj/index.htm\">人才引进</a></h3>\n          </div>\n        \n        <li>\n          <div class=\"subiconBox\">\n            <span class=\"subicon\"><img src=\"../../../images/icon3.png\"></span>\n            <h3><a href=\"../../../jz/index.htm\">捐赠</a></h3>\n          </div>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n\n    </aside>    <aside class=\"sub_right\">\n       \n <div class=\"subTitle\">\n            <div class=\"bread\"><span>                 <a href=\"../../../index.htm\">首页</a>»\n                 <a href=\"../../index.htm\">教师队伍</a>»\n                 <a href=\"../index.htm\">教师</a>»\n                 <a href=\"index.htm\">C</a>»\n        陈松蹊\n</span></div>\n            <h2>陈松蹊</h2>\n        </div>        \n        <div class=\"subcontentTotal\">\n            <div class=\"subcontent\">\n\n               <div class=\"subRetireBox\">\n\n                  \n                  <!-- 个人主页 -->\n                  <div class=\"subPersonHome\">\n                    <div class=\"subPersonHome_img\"><p><img src=\"../../../images/content/2020-08/20200828164135245700.JPG\"></p></div>\n                    <div class=\"subPersonHome_info\">\n                      <h3>陈松蹊</h3>\n                      <div class=\"subPersonHome_intro\">\n\n                        <p><strong>职称：</strong><span>教授</span></p>\n                        <p><strong>所在部门：</strong><span>统计教研室</span></p>\n                        <p class=\"last\"><strong><a href=\"http://www.songxichen.com\">个人主页</a></strong></p>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"subPersonHome_contact\">\n                        <span class=\"addr\">智华楼367</span>\n                        <span class=\"phone\"></span>\n                        <span class=\"mail\">csx at gsm pku edu cn</span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                                       <div class=\"subInfo01\">\n                    <div class=\"subInfo01_title subInfo01_title1\"><h3 class=\"t_icon2\">工作经历</h3></div>\n                    <div class=\"subInfo01_Con1\">\n                     2008 - 至今 北京大学教授、讲席教授<br>2003-2017年 Iowa State University统计系终身副教授、教授<br>2000-2003年 新加坡国立大学副教授<br>1995-2000年 澳大利亚La Trobe University讲师、高级讲师（终身教职）<br>1992-1995年 澳大利亚联邦科学院（CSIRO）海洋实验室统计师\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                   <div class=\"subInfo01\">\n                    <div class=\"subInfo01_title subInfo01_title1\"><h3 class=\"t_icon3\">代表作</h3></div>\n                    <div class=\"subInfo01_Con1\">\n                    1.\tChen, S.X. and Qin, Y-L. (2010). A Two Sample Test for Ultra High Dimensional Data with Applications to Gene Sets Testing. The Annals of Statistics, 38, 808-835. <br>2.\tChen, S.X., Li, J. and Zhong, P-S. (2019). Two-Sample and ANOVA Tests for High Dimensional Means. The Annals of Statistics, Vol. 47, No. 3, 1443-1474.<br>3.\tLiang, X., Li, S., Zhang, SY, Huang, H. and S.X. Chen (2016). PM2.5 Data Reliability, Consistency and  Air Quality Assessment in Five Chinese Cities,  Journal of Geophysical Research—Atmosphere,  121, 10220–10236.<br>4.\tXu,Z., Chen, S.X. and X. Wu (2020) Meteorological Change and Impacts on Air Pollution Results from North China, Journal of Geophysics Research-Atmosphere, 125, e2020JD032423.<br>5.\tYan, H., Zhu, YR., Gu, J., Huang, YX., Sun, HX., Zhang, XY., Wang, YT., Qiu, YM. and Chen, S.X. (2021). Better strategies for containing COVID-19 pandemic: a study of 25 countries via a vSIADR model, Proceedings of the Royal Society A, 476: 20200440. \n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"subInfo01\">\n                    <div class=\"subInfo01_title subInfo01_title1\"><h3 class=\"t_icon4\">科研项目</h3></div>\n                    <div class=\"subInfo01_Con1\">\n                     1.\t面向儿童脑发育障碍性疾病的神经机制建模与辅助诊疗算法，国家自然科学基金数学天元基金—琶洲实验室“数学与医疗健康交叉重点专项”， 12026607, 200万（+200万），2021-2022（2024），联合主持。 <br>2.\t面向管理决策大数据分析的理论与方法, 国家自然科学基金重点项目, 92046021,130万， 2021-2022，主持。 <br>3.\t变系数流行病学模型的统计推断，国家自然科学基金面上项目，12071013，58万，2021-2024，主持； <br>4.\t空气质量统计诊断模型， 国家重点研发专项项目，科技部，2016YFC0207700，1604万，2016-2020，主持；  [9]<br>5.\t大数据驱动的管理决策模型与算法，国家自然科学基金重点项目，71532001，260万， 2016-2020，主持；<br>6.\t金融连续时间随机过程的统计推断，国家自然科学基金面上项目，71371016， 56万，2014-2017，主持；<br>7.\t高维数据统计建模与分析，国家自然科学基金重点项目，1131002，220万，2012-2016，主持；\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"subInfo01\">\n                    <div class=\"subInfo01_title subInfo01_title1\"><h3 class=\"t_icon5\">主讲课程</h3></div>\n                    <div class=\"subInfo01_Con1\">\n                    本研，高等多元统计分析 （Advanced Multivariate Analysis）， 秋季<br>本研，大样本统计理论 （Asymptotic Statistics），春季。 \n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"subInfo01\">\n                    <div class=\"subInfo01_title subInfo01_title1\"><h3 class=\"t_icon7\">社会兼职</h3></div>\n                    <div class=\"subInfo01_Con1\">\n                     2019-now，Bernoulli Society，Scientific Secretary； <br>2017-now，国家统计局， 咨询委员；<br>2010-2019,  Annals of Statistics, Associate Editor, <br>2016-2020, Journal of American Statistical Association, Associate Editor <br>2016-2019，Institute of Mathematical Statistics, Council Member. \n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"subInfo01\">\n                    <div class=\"subInfo01_title subInfo01_title1\"><h3 class=\"t_icon8\">荣誉获奖</h3></div>\n                    <div class=\"subInfo01_Con1\">\n                     2009, Fellow, 美国统计学会会士.<br>2009, Fellow, Institute of Mathematical Statistics. <br>2011, Elected Member, International Statistics Institute.<br>2017, 自然科学一等奖, 教育部, 独立。<br>2018, Fellow, 美国科学促进会.  \n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n               </div>\n\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n    </aside>\n  </div>\n</article>\n<!--sub_content结束-->\n<!--content结束-->\n<!--footer开始-->\n\n<footer class=\"footer_wrap\">\n  <div class=\"footer\">\n    <div class=\"lf\">\n      <div class=\"footerList\">\n        <div class=\"footerTitle\"><h3>友情链接</h3></div>\n        <ul>\n          <l